summary:
I am passionate about Supply Chain. My studies combined with the master’s thesis, gave me a deep know how and expertise in sourcing. 

Leadership, negotiation and story telling is the area I am intersted in and keen to unleash my professional skills further. Moreover, I am passionate about languages and cross cultural environment. 

I am a good listener with excellent communication skills.  I can describe myself as an optimist, humble and loyal person with contagious enthusiasm who believes grit is key to success. I am proactive & like challenges; What challanges me, leads me to growth. 

One of my favorite quotes is : " When you achieve your goals, is not so much what you get as Who you have become in achieving them".  Henry David Thoreau
